sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as User
participant Client as WebClient
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant AuthSvc as AuthService
participant UserAuthDb as MongoUserAuth
participant Redis as RedisRefreshStore

Note over User,Redis: Luong 3 - Dang nhap va refresh token
User->>Client: Dang nhap
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/auth/login
Gateway->>AuthSvc: Forward login
AuthSvc->>UserAuthDb: Check password + lock state + verify state
alt Login hop le
  AuthSvc->>Redis: SET refresh_token:<userId>
  AuthSvc-->>Gateway: 200 access + refresh
  Gateway-->>Client: Tra token de su dung
else Chua verify / bi lock / sai mat khau
  AuthSvc-->>Gateway: 401/423
  Gateway-->>Client: Tu choi dang nhap
end

User->>Client: Xin access token moi
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/auth/refresh-token
Gateway->>AuthSvc: Forward refresh token
AuthSvc->>Redis: Validate refresh token
alt Hop le
  AuthSvc-->>Client: 200 access token moi
else Khong hop le
  AuthSvc-->>Client: 401
end
